Akpororo bu onye ilaje, Ondo State, Nigeria mana amuru ya ma zulite ya na Warri, obodo di na Delta State, Nigeria ebe o guru akwukwo
Ọrụ ya malitere dị ka onye egwu ozi ọma mpaghara ruo na 2008 mgbe ọ banyere National Comedy Challenge nke Opa Williams wee gaa n'ihu merie mpaghara Calabar nke asọmpi ahụ
N'afọ 2009, Akpororo kwagara Lagos wee zọọ asọmpi ugboro abụọ na AY's Open Mic Challenge, na-abịa nke abụọ na mbọ mbụ ya wee merie asọmpi ahụ na mbọ ya nke abụọ
Ọ gbagoro were bụrụ onye na-ewu ewu na 2013 na-eso arụmọrụ ya na ihe nkiri Basketmouth 's Laff and Jam wee gaa n'ihu na-eme n'ọtụtụ ihe nkiri ọchị gụnyere "AY Live"
Na 12 August 2014, o mere ihe ngosi ihe nkiri mbụ ya bụ "Akpororo vs Akpororo" na Shell Hall, MUSON Center
Ihe omume nwa agbọghọ ahụ hụrụ ọbịbịa nke mmemme egwu ama ama na ndị ọchị ọchị
